<emphasis id="B9626913FF92FF52FD5F88BAE457F83E" bold="true" box="[722,797,1927,1952]" pageId="67" pageNumber="68">mxp ip</emphasis>
, maxilliped inner plate; 
<emphasis id="B9626913FF92FF52FB9888BAE32DF801" bold="true" box="[1045,1127,1928,1952]" pageId="67" pageNumber="68">mxp op</emphasis>
, maxilliped outer plate.
</paragraph>
